{"tid":1954662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[告急] 老鳳需要手足支持，以免俾藍屍成功洗腦","createTime":"2020-04-02T03:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:43:45.000Z","uid":48234,"like":18,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aa1f56baae5cc495055c46e52459bac739e950c6","tid":1954662,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"嚴重分化、割蓆甚至篤魁嘅現象已經出現<br />\n<br />\n如果問題繼續惡化，老鳳將會頂唔順<br />\n強身健體之後老鳳會保護手足定係考督賊/入黑社會<br />\n取決於手足可唔可以多啲屌柒搞分化嘅仆街<br />\n<br />\n如果老鳳考咗督賊/入咗黑社會<br />\n請大家將分化狗推到最前俾老鳳打爆佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cf132316adaf43ee1b11d4d450cfda90ed0442","tid":1954662,"uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"請求手足全力支持手足<br />\n全力抵抗分化割蓆<br />\n否則老鳳將會心灰意冷，幫唔到大家抗爭，仲會幫襯藍店!<br />\n唔好迫到老鳳行呢一步!"},{"pid":"6efe78ef92ffc62285a29a7181f0c08bef1ec989","tid":1954662,"uid":223428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"我唔知可以講咩好。。。"},{"pid":"45644607a2996d1a4ee674a61c599a0780cab1e9","tid":1954662,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6efe78ef92ffc62285a29a7181f0c08bef1ec989","tid":1954662,"uid":223428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"我唔知可以講咩好。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔該，一見到分化狗幫手屌<br />\n唔好剩係block，唔夠!"},{"pid":"a996b79261e06114197d24d4bfb5823ceebcb23b","tid":1954662,"uid":183576,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"鳳鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ce37d7ea23672572d96c7423c823966ccd2e1a","tid":1954662,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"公務員仲可唔可以存在手足<br />\n取決於大家可唔可以幫手抗分化<br />\n抗分化呢一戰輸咗，包括老鳳在內公務員將會被成功洗腦<br />\n<br />\n當局稱積極研究是否要求所有公務員宣誓擁護《基本法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan